    "detail": "Smile Hotel Hakata Ekimae is only several minutes walk from Hakata Station. You can find buses, subways and trains that can get you anywhere in Fukuoka and Kyushu. It's the best for those looking for a simple accommodation with an exceptional location. The staff members are very friendly. If you arrive early, you can store your luggage there first. The room size is standard, which means that some people might find it a bit too cozy. You probably cannot fully open your luggage without placing it on your bed. But this is not a big issue I reckon. It also has laundry facilities available. You can actually monitor the laundering machine from your room, so you don't need to stay next to it for the whole process.",
